OL,5, Benefit rises among the UK's poorest   
OL,6, are failing to keep up with the cost of
OL,7, living, new figures suggest.           
OL,9,FIn the year to September, the cost of  
OL,10,Fliving rose by 8.2% among the poorest, 
OL,11,Fcompared with a 6.7% rise in benefits. 
OL,13,FThis difference might be worth roughly 
OL,14,Fan extra #15 a month to a family       
OL,15,Freceiving #900 in universal credit.    
OL,17,F"We've had two years of ministers      
OL,18,Freally wanting to maintain benefits in 
OL,19,Freal terms," said Morgan Wild of the   
OL,20,FCitizens Advice Bureau.                
